    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >《纯情的可洛妮》是由日本社团Bielograf（ビエログラフ）制作，OTAKU Plan发行的一款ADV探索游戏。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307300/extras/9beacd79ad7e3cfffe9caf1687d93751.avif?t=1770343165\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏讲述一位丧失记忆的少女可洛妮，在小村庄里的魔女的鼓励下，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >心怀对村民的感激之情，从不拒绝来自村民们的请求，逐渐成长的故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307300/extras/793e2c814c53d4e2d1a1795d70739e85.avif?t=1770343165\" width=616 height=346 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307300/extras/0d9038f80195f8640a1118c16b88daa2.avif?t=1770343165\" width=616 height=347 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307300/extras/412ecabacf46b0dbc87428cf409c1605.avif?t=1770343165\" width=780 height=78 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇◆ 换装福利 ◆◇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >部分委托需要可洛妮更换对应服装，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >纯情的可洛妮自然不会拒绝任何人的要求。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇◆ 探索剧情 ◆◇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与众多NPC对话，寻找需要帮助的人。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在不断完成帮助任务后，可洛妮能够获得更高的评价，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >同时解锁更多剧情与任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇◆ 可爱的颜艺 ◆◇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >日本知名同人画师caburi担当角色设计，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对话中将出现众多有趣颜艺，进一步渲染可爱的世界观！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◇◆ 村民的反响 ◆◇</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏搭载以村民为主体的画外音模式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在可洛妮睡着后，玩家可知晓其他人对于可洛妮的看法与评价。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏无战斗内容，且不存在复杂的操作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验恬静祥和的日常生活，感受可洛妮心境的变化与成长吧。</p>",
